headline: Genpact Named a Leader and Star Performer in Finance & Accounting by Everest Group
summary: Genpact (NYSE: G), an agentic and advanced technology solutions company, today announced that it has been recognized as both a Leader and a Star Performer in the Everest Group Finance & Accounting (F&A) Outsourcing PEAK Matrix® Assessment 2025. This latest recognition underscores Genpact's AI-first strategy and continued leadership in transforming finance operations through agentic AI and process intelligence. Read the report excerpt here.
